BT /F2 22 Tf 72 740 Td (Workout Tracker - Claude Code Handoff) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 716 Td (Expo Router React Native app for tracking workouts, exercise history, and progress locally.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 72 680 Td (What the project is about) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 660 Td (The app lets users log workouts, store sets and notes, track exercise photos, and review progress over time.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 642 Td (It supports a flexible exercise library with sports, categories, optional muscle groups, and exercises.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 624 Td (All important data is stored locally with AsyncStorage. There is no server or cloud backend in this workspace.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 72 586 Td (Main user flow) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 566 Td (Home -> Log Workout -> select sport/category/muscle/exercise -> enter sets -> save workout.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 548 Td (History and Progress read from the same saved workout records.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 530 Td (Quick Notes and the home background image are separate local features saved alongside workouts.) Tj ET
BT /F2 14 Tf 72 492 Td (Claude Code notes) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 472 Td (Category trees use parentCategoryId, with root categories stored as parentCategoryId = null.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 454 Td (Deleting a category removes its full descendant subtree.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 436 Td (Sports with requiresMuscleGroups = false skip the muscle-group step and route directly to exercises.) Tj ET
BT /F1 11 Tf 72 418 Td (The default seeded library is Gym -> Push -> Chest with sample chest exercises.) Tj ET
endstream
